item.description:
The annual Federal Hill Columbus Day Feast and Festival features live entertainment, food, and more. Let's check it out together!

I will be waiting at the Despasquale Fountain around 11:30am. The parade starts at noon. Afterwards, we can walk around together or split into smaller groups and check out the different things going on.

More event info: http://www.providence...
